               <msContents defective="false">
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipits and heading of the texts; chapter titles and the words mǝʿǝraf and kǝfl; numbers of the “tituli”; elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals; elements of the quire marks and titles in the upper margin; parts of the Canon tables; name of the owner.&#xD;
On fol. 21rb, the rubricated signs in the margin between the columns are probably the quotation markers.&#xD;
Incipits of each Gospel and Additio I are written alternately in red and black lines.</rubric>
