                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 1ra-4vb; 145va-146vb: Theological treatise composed of the quotations from the Church Fathers, unidentified.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fols. 1ra-4vb: እምቃለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቄርሎስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘለእስክንድርያ፡ ውእቱ፡ እምኈልቆሙ፡ ለአበው፡ ሊቃነ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ፳ወ፬፡ በሣልስ፡ እምድርሳናቲሁ።...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 104ra-vb, 102rb, ls.13-20: Theological discourse on the Trinity, unidentified.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fols. 104ra-vb: እጽሕፍ፡ ተዋህዶተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ይትፈጠሩ፡ ሰማያት፡ ወምድር፡ ወኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡ ነበሩ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በሠለስቱ፡ አካላት፡ ወበአሐዱ፡ መለኮት፡ አብሰ፡ ውእቱ፡ የአምር፡ እምኀበ፡ ዘወፅአ፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 234vb: Ownership note, rhymed.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 234vb: ዝመጽሐፍ፨ ዘወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፨ ዘተሣየጠ፡ በንዋዩ፨ ሶበ፡ ሀለየ፡ ፍቅረ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ከመ፡ ይትዋረሥ፡ ዘይኩን፡ ሎቱ፡ ለሕይወተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፨ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘተአገሎ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን፡ በአፈ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳው{ሎስ}፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 234vb:This (is) the book of Wäldä Giyorgis, Who acquired (it) with his own money  when he was pondering about the love of Christ, To inherit the Kingdom of Heaven, That it might be for him for the life of (his) body and soul. He who stole it or took it away shall be excommunicated by the word of Peter and Paul.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 282ra-283vb: Theological treatise on heresies, unidentified, incomplete.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fols. 282ra-283vb: ንንግርኬ፡ ዘለፋሆሙ፡ ለረሲዓን፡ ስብልያኖስ፡ ይቤ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ፩ገጽ፡ ንሕነሰ፡ ንብል፡ ፫ገጽ፡ ፩ራእይ፡ ፫አካል፡ ፩አምላክ ። ፫አስማት፡ ፩እግዚአብሔር።... </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 284ra-vb, 281va-vb: Treatise on the genealogy of Christ, unidentified.  </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 284ra-vb: ዳዊት፡ ቢወልድ፡ ናታንን፡ ሰሎሞንን፡ ናታን፡ ቢወልድ፡ ሚልኩ፡ ሹሻንን፡ አግብቶ፡ ኔሪን፡ ወልዶ፡ ሞተ፡ ሹሻንን፡ ኔሪን፡ ሕዝላ፡ ከኢዮአቄም፡ ገብታ፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Directive to the reader referring to the continuation of Text VI on fol. 145va: fol. 4v (in the bottom margin):&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign: fol. 11r.&#xD;
- Crude notes enclosed in frames: fols. 19r, 19v, 20r (the upper margin).&#xD;
- Crude note: fol. 259r (the upper margin).&#xD;
- The text of the fourth Gospel contains many corrections written interlineally and in the margins.&#xD;
- Crude note: በስ ፲፱፻፴፪ዓ፡ ም፡ ታህሣሥ፡ (in the n(ame of the Father…), 1932 year of mercy, Tahśaś): fol. 12v.</item>
